Text: Well, the video quality kind of sucks (especially for a 3cd rip), and it keeps freezing up, but thanks anyway.

I always shake my head at the futility of posters asking for seeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeds.  Those of us who seed will do so, the "hit it and quit it" assholes are already gone and won't see the post.  However, if it makes you feel better to gnash your teeth and wail at the sky, you go right ahead.  8-)
